OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLeo Varadkar says border   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpoll not appropriate at    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthis time                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A border poll on the island of Ireland 
OL,6, would "not be appropriate or right" at 
OL,7, this time, the Tanaiste (Irish deputy  
OL,8, PM) Leo Varadkar has said.             
OL,10,FMr Varadkar described the aspiration to
OL,11,Fa united Ireland as a "legitimate one".
OL,13,FHowever, he added that a border poll at
OL,14,Fthis stage would be both "divisive and 
OL,15,Fdefeated".                             
OL,17,FHe told BBC NI's Sunday Politics show  
OL,18,Fthat the focus should be on getting the
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland Assembly "up and      
OL,20,Frunning".                              
